text: "Get Dumb" is a 2007 single by Swedish DJs Axwell, Steve Angello and Sebastian Ingrosso (later known as Swedish House Mafia) along with Dutch DJ Laidback Luke. The song was also the first ever collaboration by the Swedish trio before their formation as a supergroup. ==Track listing== ==Credits== ; Produced at Groove Motel, Stockholm * Vocals – Sebastian Ingrosso * Drums – Axwell * Keyboards – Steve Angello * Percussion – Laidback Luke * Label: Big & Dirty ==Charts== Chart (2007) ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:2007 songs
title: Get Dumb
